00:18:46,678 --> 00:18:49,700
were all on Reddit because I had no home for them.

441
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:51,801
So I put everything on Reddit,

442
00:18:51,881 --> 00:18:53,562
even though they didn't have any hyperlinks.

