00:18:57,865 --> 00:19:00,006
is currently over 25 pages printed long.

446
00:19:00,787 --> 00:19:03,769
So that's an awful lot to not have any hyperlinks on,

447
00:19:04,149 --> 00:19:05,050
but you do what you can.

